q(329,"¿Cuántos jóvenes estaban en la cueva en la historia de los Ashab al-Kahf?","How many young men were in the cave in the story of Ashab al-Kahf?","شحال من شاب كان فالكهف فقصة أصحاب الكهف؟",["5","7","9","El Corán no especifica un número exacto"],["5","7","9","The Quran does not specify an exact number"],["5","7","9","القرآن ما حددش عددا بالضبط"],"El Corán no especifica un número exacto","The Quran does not specify an exact number","القرآن ما حددش عددا بالضبط","Corán y General","hard","El Corán menciona que algunos dicen 3, otros 5, otros 7, pero indica que solo Allah sabe con certeza. Hay un perro también mencionado.","The Quran mentions that some say 3, others 5, others 7, but indicates that only Allah knows for certain. A dog is also mentioned.","القرآن كيذكر أن بعض قالو 3، و بعض قالو 5، و بعض قالو 7، و لكن ما يعلمهم إلا الله. كاين أيضا كلب مذكور."),
q(330,"¿En qué Surah se relata la historia completa del Profeta Yusuf?","In which Surah is the complete story of Prophet Yusuf narrated?","فأشمن سورة تروى قصة النبي يوسف كاملة؟",["Al-Baqarah","Al-Imran","Yusuf","Al-An'am"],["Al-Baqarah","Al-Imran","Yusuf","Al-An'am"],["البقرة","آل عمران","يوسف","الأنعام"],"Yusuf","Yusuf","يوسف","Corán y General","easy","La Surah Yusuf (Capítulo 12) narra la historia completa del Profeta Yusuf y es llamada 'la mejor de las historias' en el Corán.","Surah Yusuf (Chapter 12) narrates the complete story of Prophet Yusuf and is called 'the best of stories' in the Quran.","سورة يوسف (الفصل 12) كتروي القصة الكاملة للنبي يوسف و كتسمى 'أحسن القصص' فالقرآن."),
